data.title: Corey Stoll as Dr. Eph Goodweather | The Strain | FX
data.meta_description: Corey Stoll stars in FX’s thriller The Strain as “Dr. Ephraim ‘Eph’ Goodweather.” Haunted by guilt and shame, Eph leaves NYC only to return after discovering the Master’s end game.
data.text:
Corey Stoll

as Dr. Ephraim 'Eph' Goodweather

Corey Stoll stars in FX’s thriller The Strain as “Dr. Ephraim ‘Eph’ Goodweather.” Haunted by guilt and shame, Eph leaves NYC only to return after discovering the Master’s end game.

David Bradley

as Abraham Setrakian

David Bradley stars in FX’s thriller The Strain as “Abraham Setrakian,” a man with an iron will who is faced with a critical choice: hold onto the prophecy or abandon all hope.
